# Example Hooks

You can find 1000s of hooks online. 

Simply go into LinkedIn, scroll around and save it down. 

I’ve pasted a bunch of hooks we use below:

---

How I went from 0 to [result]
I’ve read x books on [topic]. This is what it taught me.
Stop doing [process] and do this instead!
I’ve generated x$ with [process]. Want to learn how you can replicate?
