# Hook Multipliers  to Increase Perceived Value

Back in the day, someone with <10k followers could go viral with a hook like: 

- ”7 hooks that will generate 100k impressions”

But with the saturation of good hooks, you now need to increase the perceived value of the promise. You can achieve this by qualifying your statement / yourself / the subject matter

|  | Multiplier |
| --- | --- |
| Time | - I spent 100 hours
- This took me 3 years to learn 
- I analysed 2,000 videos |
| Money | - I spent £1k
- I made £100k 
- Disney generated $14bn from storytelling |
| Authority | - I spoke to 9 CEOs
- This tactic was used by AirBnB
- 20,000 CEOs have read this book |
| Recency | - Last week I
- Over the last 3 years
- Today I |

